review_en: This was the best I could find on Amazon but nowhere near as practical or good looking as my previous dish drainer. I needed one to fit over my sink and also sit on the counter next to the sink. The drainer is made of extremely sharp metal making it dangerous to move even if you’re super careful. I checked the measurements to make sure it would extend enough to fit across my sink but it’s wider than I thought, so it’s not practical to wash other items alongside. And if you move it, the plastic covers that keep it from damaging the counter fall off easily and are likely to get lost.
review_cn: 这是我在亚马逊上能找到的最好的产品，但远不如我之前的碗碟架实用或美观。我需要一个既能放在水槽上又能放在水槽旁边的台面上的架子。这个沥水架由非常锋利的金属制成，即使你非常小心，移动它也很危险。我检查了尺寸以确保它能延伸到足够覆盖我的水槽，但它比我想象的要宽，所以在旁边洗其他物品不实用。而且如果你移动它，防止它损坏台面的塑料盖很容易脱落，可能会丢失。

tags.tag_name_cn: 水槽/台面保护不足（易刮花）
tags.evidence: The drainer is made of extremely sharp metal making it dangerous to move even if you’re super careful.
